  <zone type="main">
    <line><anchor xml:id="c57-0039.01"/>these questions continually recurred but I</line>
    <line>was unable to solve them</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line rend="indent2">The volume of Plutarchs lives which I</line>
    <line>possessed contained the histories of the first</line>
    <line>founders of the ancient republics&#x2013; This book</line>
    <line>had a far different effect upon me from</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">the letters Sorrows</del> the letters of Werter. I lea<add
        place="superlinear">r</add>ned</line>
    <line>from <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">that</del>
        <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs"><del rend="strikethrough">his</del> Werter's <del
            rend="strikethrough">g</del> imaginations</add>
      </mod> despondency &amp; gloom; but Plutarch</line>
    <line>taught me high thoughts&#x2014;he elevated me above</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">m</del> the wretched sphere of my own reflections</line>
    <line>to admire &amp; love the heroes of past ages. <del rend="strikethrough">Yet</del></line>
    <line>Many things I read surpassed my unterstanding</line>
    <line>and <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">knowledge</del>
        <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add>
        <add place="superlinear">experience</add>
      </mod> I had a very <del rend="strikethrough"><unclear>t</unclear></del> confused know</line>
    <line>ledge of kingdoms &amp; wide extents of country</line>
    <line>mighty rivers and boundless seas. But I</line>
    <line>was perfectly unacquainted with towns &amp;</line>
    <line>large <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">assemblegs</del>
        <add place="superlinear">assemblages</add>
      </mod> of men. The cottage<mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">rs</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">were</del>
        <add place="superlinear">of my protectors <mod>
            <del rend="strikethrough">was</del>
            <restore type="smear_strikethrough"><del rend="strikethrough"><add place="superlinear"
                  >had been</add></del></restore>
            <del rend="smear"><add place="superlinear">was</add></del>
          </mod></add>
      </mod></line>
    <line>the <del rend="strikethrough">o</del> only school <mod>
        <add place="intralinear" hand="#pbs">in</add>
        <mod>
          <del rend="strikethrough">where</del>
          <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">which</add>
        </mod>
      </mod> I <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">had</add> studied human</line>
    <line>nature &#x2014; But this book <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">threw a new light</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">upon</del>
        <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add>
        <add place="superlinear">developed new &amp; mightier scenes of action</add>
      </mod></line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">it</del> I read of men concerned in public</line>
    <line>affairs governing <del rend="strikethrough">their species &#x2014;</del>
      <del rend="strikethrough">an</del> or masser</line>
    <line>c<del rend="strikethrough">e</del>ring their speceis. I felt the greatest ardour</line>
    <line>for virtue rise within me and abhor</line>
    <line>rence for vice <del rend="vertical_line"><unclear unit="chars" extent="1"/></del> as far
      as I understood <del rend="strikethrough">it</del> the</line>
    <line>signification of those terms relative as they</line>
    <line>were <del rend="strikethrough">only</del>, as I applied them, to pleasure</line>
    <line>and pain <mod>
        <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add>
        <add place="superlinear">alone.</add>
      </mod>. <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">with</del>
        <add place="superlinear">Induced by</add>
      </mod> these feelings <del rend="strikethrough">it may be</del></line>
    <line>I was of course led to admire peacable</line>
    <line>lawgivers Numa, Solon &amp; Lycurgus more than</line>
    <line>Romulus and Theseus. The patriarchal lives</line>
    <line>of my protectors <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">induced</del>
        <add place="superlinear"><del rend="strikethrough" instant="true">im</del> caused</add>
      </mod>
      <del rend="strikethrough">to a greater degree</del></line>
    <line>these impressions <mod>
        <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add>
        <add place="superlinear">to take a firm hold on my mind</add>
      </mod> &#x2014; perhaps if my first <mod spanTo="#c57-0039.03"/><delSpan spanTo="#c57-0039.04"
        rend="strikethrough"/>resid</line>
    <line>ence<anchor xml:id="c57-0039.04"/>
      <anchor xml:id="c57-0039.05"/><anchor xml:id="c57-0039.03"/> had been <mod>
        <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add>
        <del rend="strikethrough">with</del>
        <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">made by</add>
      </mod> a young soldier burning</line>
  </zone>
  <zone type="left_margin" corresp="#c57-0039.01">
    <addSpan spanTo="#c57-0039.02" hand="#pbs"/>
    <line>Whence</line>
    <line>did I come?</line>
    <line>What was</line>
    <line>my destination? <anchor xml:id="c57-0039.02"/></line>
